There are 2 bdrms, 2.5 baths, a study, living rm, family rm, kitchen and formal dining rm in the main house. Upon entering you immediately notice the red oak floor and a basement hatch in the entry flooring. This door is one way to access the full basement as well as 2 doors in the backyard. Gorgeous and intricately designed wallpaper throughout the house, including the ceilings, is done with exquisite flair. Hanging delicately designed woodwork provides a sense of room separation. Kitchen is light, airy and complete with 6 gas burner Wolf range, dishwasher, microwave, 2nd oven and refrigerator. All bathrooms have flush toilets with elevated water tanks. Electrical and plumbing systems have been updated. Stained glass windows in several rooms. The front and back yards are landscaped and well kept. Sit out on brick patio and enjoy the water fountain!

3rd Party Synd. Remarks: Stately Craftsman home featuring original natural wood floors, decorative windows, beveled leaded glass cupboard doors and grand built-ins. The enclosed patio is a perfect area to greet guests or sit for a quiet read. The large dining room has a coffered ceiling and is ideal for entertaining guests. Four large bedrooms are complete with large walk-in closets. A spacious upstairs bathroom features a freestanding bathtub and overhead shower. Additional features include: two sets of small paned double-doors, six wood pocket doors, sconces, and a finished storage area in basement. Two driveways with extra parking leading to the detached garage. The extra space and bonus room off the kitchen can easily be designed as new bathrooms or office space. Improvements include new interior and exterior painting and new roof. This beauty, set in the tree-lined streets of historic Midtown West, has not been remodeled out of its elegant charm and is 2 blocks from Dameron Hospital and the Cathedral of the Annunciation. 3rd Party Synd. Remarks: Adorable move in ready home! Remodeled kitchen with quartz countertops, new stove, dishwasher, and microwave. Remodeled bath, new roof on house and detached garage, new exterior paint, newer electrical wiring throughout house and garage. Central heat & air, insulated attic, and vinyl siding help keep energy costs down. Wood floors in living room and bedroom, new lino in kitchen and bath in 2021. Bonus room can be 2nd bedroom or office and has heat/air and clothes closet. Window coverings and blinds included. Large backyard is superb for entertaining. Three large trees on west side of property provide excellent shade and keep house cool in the summer. Full basement will accommodate all of your storage needs. 1 car garage with opener. Long driveway and paved surface in backyard provide parking for 5-6 cars/possible RV parking. Close to bus lines and a 20 minute walk to the Miracle Mile. Excellent rental property. Sale includes the following items: 5 piece bedroom set, leather couch, new twin bed, computer desk, 60 wall-mounted TV, dinette set, refrigerator, chest freezer, washing machine, credenza, and curio cabinet. Move in ready...just bring your clothes!
